WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:05.200
Wife, let's get along

2
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.166
Don't you have to go to work? Are you busy with work?

3
00:00:07.166 --> 00:00:08.700
Idle with me every day

4
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:12.300
Before the storm

5
00:00:12.766 --> 00:00:13.766
All very quiet

6
00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:16.600
Is something about to happen?

7
00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:18.066
Lily, I won't tell you.

8
00:00:18.066 --> 00:00:19.200
No matter what happens

9
00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:21.500
You have to keep yourself safe, you know?

10
00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:24.000
Don't worry, wife.

11
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:26.100
Here comes the storm

12
00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:27.600
It's not us who are hurt

13
00:00:27.966 --> 00:00:29.566
It's their Xu family

14
00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:31.700
After the storm

15
00:00:32.333 --> 00:00:34.166
The Xu family will cease to exist

16
00:00:35.466 --> 00:00:36.266
Li Yi

17
00:00:37.733 --> 00:00:39.900
Mr. Huang, why are you here?

18
00:00:40.166 --> 00:00:42.800
What's the matter?

19
00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:48.466
Wife, I'll go out first

20
00:00:48.466 --> 00:00:49.366
Be right back

21
00:00:49.366 --> 00:00:50.600
Well, get busy.

22
00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:52.600
You don't have to come to me every day, Mr. Wang

23
00:00:53.800 --> 00:00:55.000
Let's have tea first

24
00:00:55.466 --> 00:00:56.300
What's the matter?

25
00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:00.966
Tell me slowly, how can I be in the mood to drink tea now?

26
00:01:02.266 --> 00:01:04.800
The Xu family has been modest recently

27
00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:06.800
I won several major projects in succession

28
00:01:08.066 --> 00:01:09.633
Go on like this

29
00:01:10.300 --> 00:01:14.066
We have no place in the river

30
00:01:16.566 --> 00:01:17.366
Mr. Huang

31
00:01:18.266 --> 00:01:19.800
Promised actions

32
00:01:19.966 --> 00:01:22.200
It's all from me

